From ea5c48315743e5981253bc73546ece5f0aedd8c6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Chao Yu <chao@kernel.org>
Date: Fri, 30 Dec 2022 23:43:32 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 049/234] f2fs: fix to avoid NULL pointer dereference in
