@@ -49,16 +49,23 @@ Contact:	"Jaegeuk Kim" <jaegeuk.kim@samsung.com>
 Description:	Controls the in-place-update policy.
 		updates in f2fs. User can set:
 
-		====  =================
-		0x01  F2FS_IPU_FORCE
-		0x02  F2FS_IPU_SSR
-		0x04  F2FS_IPU_UTIL
